subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Creighton, the No. 7 seed in the Midwest, hit 11 of 12 free throws in the final 1 minutes 42 seconds to fend off No. 10 Cincinnati and secure a spot against Duke in the Round of 32.
